{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@objc"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"spaceRowGapAction"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSTokensSemantic05SpaceB5Tokena","text":"SpaceSemanticToken"},{"kind":"text","text":" { "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"get"},{"kind":"text","text":" }"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}]}],"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemealertcomponenttokensprovider\/spacerowgapaction"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeAlertComponentTokensProvider"]]},"metadata":{"title":"spaceRowGapAction","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"spaceRowGapAction"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSTokensSemantic05SpaceB5Tokena","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"SpaceSemanticToken"}],"extendedModule":"OUDSThemesOrange","externalID":"s:16OUDSThemesOrange0B33ThemeAlertComponentTokensProviderC17spaceRowGapActionSdvp","role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"Theme Orange"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Property","symbolKind":"property"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Has for value token spaces.rowGap2xsmall"}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeAlertComponentTokensProvider\/spaceRowGapAction","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"sections":[],"references":{"ic_theme_orange.png":{"type":"image","alt":null,"identifier":"ic_theme_orange.png","variants":[{"url":"\/images\/OUDSThemesOrange\/ic_theme_orange.png","traits":["1x","light"]}]},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange":{"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","title":"Theme Orange","images":[{"type":"icon","identifier":"ic_theme_orange.png"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The Orange theme overrides some tokens from the basic "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and should be seen as the default theme for the OUDS library with the Orange brand colors for example."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange","role":"collection"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeAlertComponentTokensProvider":{"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeAlertComponentTokensProvider"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component  tokens of alert"}]},{"type":"text","text":" for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"alert"}]},{"type":"text","text":" objects like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSAlert"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllAlertComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeAlertComponentTokensProvider","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AlertComponentTokens"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"alert"}]},{"type":"text","text":" through any "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Alert","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" components tokens are defined with semantic tokens of borders ("},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllBorderSemanticTokensProviders"},{"type":"text","text":"),"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"spaces (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":") and sizes (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSizeSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"type":"topic","role":"symbol","title":"OrangeThemeAlertComponentTokensProvider","kind":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeAlertComponentTokensProvider"}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemealertcomponenttokensprovider","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeAlertComponentTokensProvider"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeAlertComponentTokensProvider/spaceRowGapAction":{"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"spaceRowGapAction"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"SpaceSemanticToken","preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSTokensSemantic05SpaceB5Tokena"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Has for value token spaces.rowGap2xsmall"}],"type":"topic","role":"symbol","title":"spaceRowGapAction","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemealertcomponenttokensprovider\/spacerowgapaction","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeAlertComponentTokensProvider\/spaceRowGapAction"}}}